{"tid":1994900,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"你班教育界同社福界可唔可以俾啲良心","createTime":"2020-04-29T20:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T08:01:12.000Z","uid":220460,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"addc477a50c5f61f5d35393c5d66ff6196f18a1e","tid":1994900,"uid":220460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T20:43:02.000Z","msg":"成長環境對小朋友個影響大到我地想像唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n生仔唔需要考牌姐，社工同老師都要考牌㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然都只係打份工，<br />\n但呢份工既責任同意義何其重大，下一代係點就睇你地點導同點教<br />\n老師同社工都係導人向善既職業<br />\n你地個心可唔可以都善良啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以係考牌之前諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：細細個就冇左老豆，老母有躁狂症，成日發癲，一發作就鬧我同dum爛屋企啲嘢，搞到我成個童年都活係恐懼之下<br />\n中學搵過社工，但個社工好撚hea，唔多理我個case<br />\n成年之後先發現自己有嚴重抑鬱加焦慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5917addec8510d0e04d051f69075c086aa65cfc0","tid":1994900,"uid":120400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T20:57:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警死全家</span>"},{"pid":"3ecb61465bf2114ed5a57a1a0dc15410cd35e9a1","tid":1994900,"uid":259532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T21:16:53.000Z","msg":"導人向善？"},{"pid":"debac263720903c927164e4b3c2d307035a73ad1","tid":1994900,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T00:06:08.000Z","msg":"無辦法，做又36唔做又36，無誘因去提升工作表現，甚至用把口來做野"},{"pid":"37b859cb7ca5a4e70062b9a59ef9c4afbb19dc39","tid":1994900,"uid":58851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:01:12.000Z","msg":"社工=有牌呃飯食"}]}